    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Deep Magic: </strong>shadow</em><br>You conjure a shadow mastiff from the plane of shadow. This creature obeys your verbal commands to aid you in battle or to seek out a specific creature. It has the body of a large dog with a smooth black coat, 2 feet high at the shoulder and weighing 200 pounds.<br>The mastiff is friendly to you and your companions. Roll initiative for the mastiff; it acts on its own turn. It obeys simple, verbal commands from you, within its ability to act. Giving a command takes no action on your part.<br>The mastiff disappears when it drops to 0 hit points or when the spell ends.",
